The invention provides a continuous melting furnace capable of controlling wall thickness at high precision. A core bar is positioned above a former, and the top of the core bar is fixed with a core bar fixing device; the outer edge of the core bar fixing device is fixed with the inner wall of a crucible of the continuous melting furnace; and the length of the core bar is 1/3 of that of the crucible or below. According to the invention, the precise positioning of the former and the core bar can be realized by the core bar fixing device, so that materials can be uniformly discharged, thereby solving the problem that the wall thickness is nonuniform due to instability or swaying of the core bar and former caused by flow of a quartz solution and high temperature deformation, and ensuring that the wall thickness of a formed quartz tube is uniform. Besides, the continuous melting furnace provided by the invention also comprises the core bar fixing device, so that the clearance between the core bar and the former is uniform, thereby solving the wall offset problem of the quartz tube, ensuring that the wall thickness of the quartz tube is uniform and improving the geometric precision in quartz tube production.
